categories: Category:Articles that are known by a nickname

nodes.text: "Frog Man" was the husband of Frog Lady who lived during the New Republic Era. He found a home on the moon of Trask where he told his wife to come. When Din Djarin succeeded in transporting his wife to Trask, Frog Man was very grateful and shook Djarin's hand. Later, Frog Man and his wife looked after Grogu as a favor to Djarin while he went on a mission, at their new home.
